# Export header contract

- Column order in `Export.HEADER` and `CullExport.HEADER` (`core/`) is relied on by Apps Script handlers.
- Never reorder or rename columns without updating `core/`, `backend/shared.js`, and `backend/test/`.
- `shared.js` is source of truth for backend logic; mirror to `shared.gs` on deploy.
